elieve in making friends not contacts we believe in giving not taking we believe in helping others before helping yourself we are truly passionate about helping founders entrepreneurs and startups succeed we intend to make their startup journey less lonely more connected and more memorable community milestones  volunteers  events since   minutes of free education  total minutes watched  members and attendees start a chapter sponsor an event suggest a speaker become a writer values global community for entrepreneurs  cities  countries  entrepreneurs login startup grind values follow us startup grind toggle navigation global conference startups events upcoming eventsglobal conference get involved discussionssponsor an eventsuggest a speakerbecome a writer videos startup grindhosts sanju bansal cofounder of microstrategy washington dc august     pm about this event founded in  by michael j saylor and sanju k bansal microstrategy develops and sells business intelligence mobile software and cloudbased services for some of the top fortune  companies and technology companies in the world including facebook ebay and yahoo  microstrategy was one of the first companies to pioneer datadriven enterprises with business intelligence and now is enhancing big data capabilities with its army of data scientists  it is a public traded company on the nasdaq mstr with almost  million in revenues with  employees worldwide  mr bansal received an sb in electrical engineering from the massachusetts institute of technology and an ms in computer science from the johns hopkins university hear this incredible ragstorichestoragstoriches story from the perspective of this famous and humble dc area founder  also we will talk about his insights to big data in the enterprises social media and mobile     speaker sanju bansal cofounder of microstrategy founded in  by michael j saylor and sanju k bansal microstrategy develops and sells business intelligence mobile software and cloudbased services for s