uary  vestmark offers a technology platform to enable broker dealers investment managers rias bank trusts and other financial firms to deliver wealth management and advisory solutions verato as a member of the board of directors since january  verato is a saasbased platform that cleans updates and links customer records within and across systems previous boards microstrategy as vicechairman of the board of directors bansal served on the microstrategy board from september  to november  cvent nyse cvt as cofounder and member of the cvent board of directors since  providing the seed capital for the eventmanagement software company bansal is credited with helping cvent navigate the burst of the dotcom bubble and more recently pushing the firm to expand into mobile and social applications in july  cvent secured  million in venture capital financing from new enterprise associates and insight venture partners with greenspring associates also participating on august   cvent had its initial public offering with a price of  and bansal owned approximately  million shares or  of the company on april   cvent announced that the company was acquired by vista equity partners for  billion philanthropyedit in  bansal established the sanju k bansal foundation the foundation tagline is helping people help themselves through improved access to information the foundation is known for its financial sponsorship of wamu  american university radio wamu  is the leading public radio station for npr news and information in the greater washington dc area the bansal foundation contributes to organizations including the washington humane society the network for teaching entrepreneurship nfte upakar indianamerican scholarship foundation the kailash goyal foundation the global india fund and wolf trap national park for the performing arts in may  the kailash goyal foundation with aid from the bansal foundation opened the jk shanti charitable clinic a free clinic to support the medical needs of the villagers and laborers near the indian town of panchkula the clinic treats approximately  people a year bansal served on the board of directors for wolf trap foundation for the performing arts from  to  located near vienna virginia wolf trap is the only national park dedicated to the performing arts recognition and awardsedit in  bansal received the washington business journals outstanding directors award for his work with cvent in   and  bansal was named one of the washingtonians  top tech titans a list honoring the top  leaders of washington dcs tech world in  he was named one of the washingtonians style setters referencesedit  salter chuck  the reeducation of an internet ceo fast company retrieved    form k for microstrategy inc yahoo finance  retrieved    cvent announces pricing of initial public offering herald online  retrieved    forbes profile of sanju bansal forbes  retrieved    martin kady ii in the shadows washington business journal november    chuck salter the reeducation of an internet ceo fast company december    carbasho tracy  turnarounds are possible with strong guiding hand indus business journal retrieved    glasser jeff  from the ground up and up the washington post retrieved    initial public offerings key data nasdaq  retrieved    kaplan david a  microstrategys boy king grows up fortune retrieved    carbasho tracy  turnarounds are possible with strong guiding hand indus business journal retrieved    hilzenrath david s  for microstrategy a matter of timing the washington post retrieved    lau debra  forbes faces michael saylor forbes retrieved    historical prices microstrategy inc mstr yahoo finance retrieved    flook bill   years in  microstrategy restated two years of earnings washington business journal retrieved    jeff clabaugh microstrategy reorganizes management washington business journal october    microstrategy about us  microstrategy announces fourth quarter  financial results  microstrategy about us  advisory board company abco sanj